java.lang.Object

CharacterController, GameMainSceneController, GlobalLobbyController, PreviousGameController, SetupChoiceSceneController, WelcomeController
public abstract class FXMLController extends Object
FXMLController represents a generic controller of a javafx scene or sub scene.
